## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **belimumab Benlysta 2011 + 2020 LN expansion** = first FDA SLE biologic in 50+ year. BAFF/BLyS soluble ligand neutralization. 2020 LN BLISS-LN trial → renal indication. quantum-VQE 의 ligand-mAb binding scaffold fit.
2. **anifrolumab Saphnelo 2021** = first FDA IFNAR1 mAb. TULIP-1 + TULIP-2 BICLA composite endpoint. type I IFN signature high subgroup 우월. quantum-VQE 의 receptor-mAb interface 가 next-gen small-molecule lead.
3. **voclosporin Lupkynis 2021** = first FDA novel CNI for LN — AURORA-1 trial. cyclosporin analog + 단일 isomer + dose-flat PK. mycophenolate background + voclosporin add = renal response 우월. quantum-VQE 의 calcineurin-cyclophilin interface scaffold.
4. **CAR-T anti-CD19 SLE (Mougiakakos 2021 NEJM)** = first 5-환자 refractory SLE drug-free remission report. UPENN + 한국 K + Erlangen group 후속. paradigm shift — "living drug" autoimmune extension. CRS/ICANS 부작용 + long-term safety open.
5. **iberdomide + dazodalibep + ianalumab + telitacicept 2024+ pipeline** = SLE Phase 2/3 polypharmacy. CRBN-modulator (IMID-class) + CD40L + BAFF-R + APRIL/BAFF dual. quantum-VQE 의 PPI + degron + ligand pocket 다중 fit.
6. **deucravacitinib Sotyktu 2022 psoriasis → SLE Phase 3 PAISLEY** = first FDA TYK2 allosteric pseudokinase inhibitor. JH2 domain selective — JAK1-3 spare. SLE PAISLEY Phase 3 진행 중. quantum-VQE 의 pseudokinase allosteric leverage.
7. **hydroxychloroquine Plaquenil 50+ year** = 1L 표준 — disease-modifying. TLR7-9 endosomal acidification 차단. retinal toxicity dose-dependent. 만성 lifelong administration.
8. **mycophenolate vs cyclophosphamide LN induction** = NIH 1986 cyclophosphamide pulse vs 2005 ALMS mycophenolate non-inferior. 임신 + 한국 K-LN MMF 1L 표준화. cyclophosphamide IV pulse 만성 severe + 응급.
9. **steroid-sparing race (dazucorilant + iberdomide + voclosporin)** = corticosteroid 만성 toxicity (cushingoid + 골다공증 + 백내장 + 감염) 회피 race. 만성 SLE 환자 lifelong taper open.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, SLE + LN 임상 의미 한정. 임신 + 청소년 + 영유아 SLE subgroup 특히 underrepresented.

